job.title: Indian Army Short Service Commission Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online For Various  Vacancies in India
job.body:
Total Vacancies: Various

Name of the Posts:

  • Short Service Commission( NT)

Description

New Central Government Jobs for graduates have been published by the Indian Army for the vacancies of SSC. If you are searching for a government job all over India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of SSC, from 06.05.2021, and till 04.06.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online

Educational qualification to apply :

  • To apply for an SSC in Indian ARMY vacancies in India, your Graduation must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply for these posts is 06.05.2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these posts is 04.06.2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 27  years old. 

Indian Army SSC Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is AS PER NORMS.

How to apply for Indian Army Short Service Commission Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the SSC. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of the Indian Army and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by the Indian Army.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
